{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7280873610","title":"给江唐的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"549ea12d84","index":0,"year":1949,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"7280873610"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"2317b8239d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"江唐（1878-1960），号云，福建长汀人，法学家。1949年春和颜惠庆、章士钊、邵力子等以私人资格北上同中国共产党商议和谈问题。同年秋，应邀参加中国人民政治协商会议第一届全体会议。建国后，曾任中央人民政府政治法律委员会委员、上海市文史研究馆副馆长。"},{"id":"d54e1b6663","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"颜俊人，即颜骏人（1877—1950），名惠庆，上海人。曾任北洋政府国务总理、外交总长和国民党政府驻美公便、驻苏大便。1949年秋，应邀参加中国人民政治协商会议第一届全体会议。建国后，任华东军政委员会副主席，中央人民政府政治法律委员会委员。"},{"id":"2db131b885","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指江康向毛泽东推荐法学界的许藻熔一事。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5219c37339","type":"title","text":"给江唐的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610"},{"id":"2317b8239d","type":"paragraph","text":"翊云先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610"},{"id":"d54e1b6663","type":"paragraph","text":"大示敬悉。时局发展甚快，新政协有迅速召开之必要，拟请先生及颜俊人先生参加，不识可以成行否？许先生事，已喔法学方面的同志注意延接。率复。敬颂道安！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610"},{"id":"2db131b885","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610"},{"id":"ca2a4411d2","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610"}],"page":{"id":"e39733a8a1","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"7280873610","start":152,"end":152}}}},"__N_SSG":true}